  npcPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bff513e9a16e7fc4a90351bd098a6f78, type: 3}
  dialogueLines:
  - Tracks led me here. Forest, cabins... makes more sense than that other place
  - I'm tracking something small. Fast. Shouldn't survive out here
  - Light steps... uneven. Like it's panicking
  - ....Doesn't belong in this kind of cold
  - And then there's those two... always watching. Weird kids. Keep talking nonsense,
    walking in circles
  - They're messing up the trail. Or.... something is
  - MAYBE IT'S JUST YOU!?1?
